	<div class="unit whole help-instructions">
		<h3>
			How do I accept an assignment?
		</h3>
		<hr>
		<p>
			Select <a class="accepting-link" href="/mobile/assignments/available">"Available Work"</a> from the home screen.
		</p>
		<p>
			You can select either "Invited" or "Work Feed" to see assignments that are available for you to accept.
			Invited means a company has sent you an invitation to apply to an assignment. WorkFeed shows you work you can apply to
			in your area.
		</p>
		<p>
			Once you have found the assignment you would like to accept/apply too, click on the title of that assignment.
		</p>
		<p>
			Review the budget details, description and date/time. Then scroll to the bottom of the page and click on Accept/Apply.
			You can also find these options by clicking the navigation icon in the top right corner, or by swiping from right to left
			on your phone.
		</p>
	</div>
